OL,3,CDirector of Public Health: Gambling
OL,4,C'likely' on the rise in Guernsey
OL,6,FGambling issues in are "likely" to be
OL,7,Fgetting worse, according to the
OL,8,Fisland's Director of Public Health.
OL,10,FIt comes as a study, carried out pre-
OL,11,Fpandemic, found nearly 80% of
OL,12,Fislanders do some form of the activity.
OL,14,FHowever, Dr Nicola Brink says the
OL,15,Fimpact of the pandemic, as well as the
OL,16,Fcost of living, means that figure
OL,17,Fcould now be higher.
