OL,4,C'likely' on the rise in Guernsey
OL,6,FIt found the most popular activity
OL,7,Famong islanders was the Channel
OL,8,FIslands Christmas Lottery, followed by
OL,9,Fscratch cards.
OL,11,FThe report recommends raising
OL,12,Fawareness of the issues around
OL,13,Fgambling in schools, introducing more
OL,14,Fsupport for those who need help, and
OL,15,Fconsidering the introduction of
OL,16,Fpolicies that could help vulnerable
OL,17,Fislanders.
